# Controller Key Mapping References

## Axes Mapping

| **Axis**               | **Index** | **Default Value** | **Range**              |
|------------------------|-----------|-------------------|------------------------|
| **Left Thumbstick X**  | 0         | 0                 | Left = 1 / Right = -1  |
| **Left Thumbstick Y**  | 1         | 0                 | Up = 1 / Down = -1     |
| **Right Thumbstick X** | 2         | 0                 | Left = 1 / Right = -1  |
| **Right Thumbstick Y** | 3         | 0                 | Up = 1 / Down = -1     |
| **Right Trigger (RT)** | 4         | 1                 | Press Down = -1        |
| **Left Trigger (LT)**  | 5         | 1                 | Press Down = -1        |
| **D-Pad Horizontal**   | 6         | 0                 | Left = 1 / Right = -1  |
| **D-Pad Vertical**     | 7         | 0                 | Up = 1 / Down = -1     |

### Axes Index to Key

| **Index** | **Axis**              |
|-----------|-----------------------|
| 0         | Left Thumbstick X     |
| 1         | Left Thumbstick Y     |
| 2         | Right Thumbstick X    |
| 3         | Right Thumbstick Y    |
| 4         | Right Trigger (RT)    |
| 5         | Left Trigger (LT)     |
| 6         | D-Pad Horizontal      |
| 7         | D-Pad Vertical        |

## Buttons Mapping

| **Button** | **Index** | **Description**       |
|------------|-----------|-----------------------|
| **A**      | 0         |                       |
| **B**      | 1         |                       |
| **X**      | 3         |                       |
| **Y**      | 4         |                       |
| **LS**     | 6         | Left Stick Button     |
| **RS**     | 7         | Right Stick Button    |
| **LT**     | 8         | Left Trigger          |
| **RT**     | 9         | Right Trigger         |
| **Back**   | 10        |                       |
| **Start**  | 11        |                       |

### Buttons Index to Key

| **Index** | **Button**         |
|-----------|--------------------|
| 0         | A                  |
| 1         | B                  |
| 3         | X                  |
| 4         | Y                  |
| 6         | LS (Left Stick)    |
| 7         | RS (Right Stick)   |
| 8         | LT (Left Trigger)  |
| 9         | RT (Right Trigger) |
| 10        | Back               |
| 11        | Start              |

**Note:**  
- **Button Index 2** is currently unassigned.
- The exact mappings may vary depending on the joystick hardware and configuration. Always verify with your specific device.

## Additional Information

- **Dual Mapping:** Each mapping table provides both `Key -> Index` and `Index -> Key` for easy reference.
- **Default Values:** Indicates the default state of each axis when no input is provided.
- **Range:** Specifies the possible values for each axis based on joystick movement or button press.